   <text>
      <body>
         <div>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-1a.1" xml:lang="en">[...] you? (?) </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-1a.2" xml:lang="en">So he did not comply. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-1a.3" xml:lang="en">Zheng Yin said: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-1a.4" xml:lang="en">"Heaven sent misfortune to the state of Chu </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-1a.5" xml:lang="en">You hurried out, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-1a.6" xml:lang="en">looking fiercely (?) </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-1a.7" xml:lang="en">losing your reputation </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-1a.8" xml:lang="en">therefore nobody recognized you (as a worthy man?) </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-2a.1" xml:lang="en">[...] the woman (?) praying Heaven for good luck. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-2a.2" xml:lang="en">Until King Zhao died </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-2a.3" xml:lang="en">he encountered the King waiting (for him?) at Sui </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-2a.4" xml:lang="en">he fought in Shi, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-2a.5" xml:lang="en">he fought in Jin, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-2a.6" xml:lang="en">he fought in Zhang [...] </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-2a.7" xml:lang="en">?? </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-3a.1" xml:lang="en">he fought three times and three times he was caught prisoner </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-3a.2" xml:lang="en">and yet the people did not think of him as courageous </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-3a.3" xml:lang="en">until he returned to his country </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-3a.4" xml:lang="en">and the crown was taken by the king </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-3a.5" xml:lang="en">and yet the people did not find it beautiful. </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-4a.1" xml:lang="en">Until the disaster of Duke Bai </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-4a.2" xml:lang="en">when he heard that the XX and the YY were already dead </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-4a.3" xml:lang="en">and went to Ying. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-4a.4" xml:lang="en">All the elders of Ye advised him: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-4a.5" xml:lang="en">"It is not admissible, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-4a.6" xml:lang="en">you must (go) with an army." </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-5a.1" xml:lang="en">Ye Gong Zi Gao said: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-5a.2" xml:lang="en">If I don't get the king (back), </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-5a.3" xml:lang="en">I must die, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-5a.4" xml:lang="en">what is an army for?" </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-5a.5" xml:lang="en">Then he rode five fast carriages </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-5a.6" xml:lang="en">and reached Ying. </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-6a.1" xml:lang="en">When he arrived, and had not yet got the king back </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-6a.2" xml:lang="en">and consort Zhao told him: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-6a.3" xml:lang="en">"the sons of the former king are assembled outside </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-6a.4" xml:lang="en">your words are wrong </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-6a.5" xml:lang="en">in the past Zhou (?) why not choosing one and setting him on the throne (?) </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-6a.6" xml:lang="en">Once the state has a king, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-6a.7" xml:lang="en">would it be all fine? </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-7a.1" xml:lang="en">Ye Gong Zi Gao said: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-7a.2" xml:lang="en">??? </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-7a.3" xml:lang="en">why implementing a delusional policy (?) </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-7a.4" xml:lang="en">and put together these two as lords of the state </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-7a.5" xml:lang="en">one lord would still treat him (the other) as too young </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-7a.6" xml:lang="en">I absolutely fear that the lord might not leave to the end of his days, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-7a.7" xml:lang="en">and (so not be able to) protect the state </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-8a.1" xml:lang="en">after he spoke, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-8a.2" xml:lang="en">he summoned (?) priest Gu (?) to stop her. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-8a.3" xml:lang="en">Great priest Cai stopped her </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-8a.4" xml:lang="en">The sovereign should (?) put on his vest and royal crown </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-8a.5" xml:lang="en">and go out and approach great priest Cai with a ritual walk, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-8a.6" xml:lang="en">kowtow twice and say: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-8a.7" xml:lang="en">With today's ritual walk, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-8a.8" xml:lang="en">we will either lose the state, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-8a.9" xml:lang="en">or obtain it (for good) </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-8a.10" xml:lang="en">Great (priest) Cai [...] </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-9a.1" xml:lang="en">Quieted the turmoil. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-9a.2" xml:lang="en">He rewarded him with one hundred zhen of land in the western fields (?) </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-9a.3" xml:lang="en">He declined saying: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-9a.4" xml:lang="en">"Your majesty would (in this way) interfere with my service (to you) (?) </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-9a.5" xml:lang="en">I must not permit it." </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-9a.6" xml:lang="en">He declined and did not accept the reward. </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-10a.1" xml:lang="en">The king appointed him as XX, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-10a.2" xml:lang="en">he declined. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-10a.3" xml:lang="en">The king appointed him as YY, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-10a.4" xml:lang="en">he declined, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-10a.5" xml:lang="en">"Given the distance from (my lands in) Ye, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-10a.6" xml:lang="en">I would not be able to take care of them." </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-10a.7" xml:lang="en">Then he served as provisional YY, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-10a.8" xml:lang="en">not assuming the actual position </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-10a.9" xml:lang="en">and the people did not see it as an honor. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0086_tls_001-10a.10" xml:lang="en"> </seg>
                </p>

         </div>
      </body>
